::Terrataur::
       She quickly tells him the name of their group (I haven't decided what 
it is yet so don't ask.)  "We came here looking for our comrade Aerotaur.  He 
was wounded severely by our former commander and launched in a stasis pod.  
Which we tracked to this planet where we found him.  When we were complete we 
were a gestalt team. That is the other reason we needed to track him down.  
Aerotaur was our second in command, before the incident.  We need him to help 
us take on our former commander and fix his programming."  She looked grimly 
at Windlord.

--part1_30.1a67ab63.28cc3bc3_boundary
